text: From mulpol efter ðe siche to ðe forde.
Of ðe forde up long gerdes into ðe weie.
On oðe stude of rodberdes huse in ðe strete onlong gerdes to waringes rudinge ðonene onlon gerdes to ðe imbe ac.
From ðe imbe ac onlon gerdes to ðe surftro.
From ðe <surftreo> onlong gerdes to caue rudinge.
Ðenene onlong gierdes to ða linde.
Ðenene onlong gierdes to henne lega ðennene dunewardes onlong gerdes to hole fiche.
Ðonene uppard hole fiche to ðam hauede.
From ðam hauede onlong gierdes to ðam stodfolde.
From ðam stodfolda onlong ðe olde weie to Edwines huse at ðe fenne.
Ðonene onlong gierdes to wibbe cumbes hauede.
Ðenene onlong gierdes under dune to ðe wulf putte.
Of ðe wulf putte onlong gierdes to totes <stige>.
Ðonene onlong gierde to ðam eowe.
